data.description: Seller offering up to $5,000 toward Buyers closing costs for contract that closes on or before 1/30/24, time is of the essence! New Carpet in all 3 Bedrooms and new laminate floor in bonus room installed January 2024. Electric Panel upgraded to 100 amp in January 2024. Hot off the press is this perfect starter ranch with just over 1,400 square feet. 3 bed, 1 full bath, 1 half bath. Kettering schools. Neighborhood has sidewalks and street lights. Oversized detached two car garage is perfect for storage/workshop! Kitchen features stainless appliances and a large island. Privacy fenced yard.  Furnace and AC replaced in 2021. 10 min to The Greene and I-675 and I-75
